1
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:32,260
♫  With no specter to cut off the waves  ♫

2
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:39,900
♫  With no halo bestowed by heaven  ♫

3
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:49,920
♫  I should admit I was born ordinary  ♫

4
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:55,210
♫  But I'm not resigned to the silence on stage  ♫

5
00:00:57,200 --> 00:01:00,960
♫  Break it down, I'm taking over now  ♫

6
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,140
♫  Tough it out, that's what I'm all about  ♫

7
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:08,600
♫  We are destined to break through a mental wall  ♫

8
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:11,980
♫  To unlock a ray of light  ♫

9
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:16,260
♫  We know there will be infinite waves  ♫

10
00:01:16,260 --> 00:01:19,540
♫  Getting in my way  ♫

11
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:23,780
♫  They will build up into roads that enable me to climb high and see far  ♫

12
00:01:23,780 --> 00:01:27,640
♫  To test me, inspire me, make me, and give me courage  ♫

13
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:31,480
♫  I'm ultimately the master  ♫

14
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:35,410
♫  Of my own destiny  ♫

15
00:01:35,410 --> 00:01:38,020
[Psychologist]

16
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:41,740
