00:40:38,330 --> 00:40:40,063
Feifei,

520
00:40:41,380 --> 00:40:43,220
do you know?

521
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:48,000
Although I created your life, you don't belong to me.

522
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:50,350
You belong to yourself.

523
00:40:55,050 --> 00:40:57,050
You can…

524
00:40:58,670 --> 00:41:02,760
get rid of all the depressions and bondages

525
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:05,280
to create your own world,

526
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:08,450
a world that you want.

527
00:41:09,250 --> 00:41:12,200
This is what I most want to give you,

528
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:15,110
freedom I've craved for all my life.

529
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:21,770
I really hope you can be the man you want to be,

530
00:41:21,770 --> 00:41:27,020
be a man as free as the heaven and the sea.

531
00:41:29,870 --> 00:41:31,703
This is

532
00:41:34,660 --> 00:41:38,420
the only thing I can give you.

533
00:41:42,570 --> 00:41:44,420
Do you get it?

534
00:41:52,240 --> 00:41:53,873
Yes.

535
00:42:04,870 --> 00:42:07,630
Mom, I love you so much.

536
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:10,230
Mommy loves you so much too.

537
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:13,810
I seem to have put in soy sauce three times.

538
00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:15,120
It's OK. It's very tasty.

539
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:16,920
Please try it too.

540
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:21,810
Your son is handsome, so anything looks good on him.

541
00:42:21,810 --> 00:42:25,190
How could there be a mother who doesn't love her child?

542
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:52,311
Speaking of which, I have a craving for candies.

543
00:42:52,970 --> 00:42:54,720
What shall we do?

544
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:57,360
You can't eat that many candies now.

545
00:42:57,360 --> 00:43:00,150
Now you've even started to disobey me?

546
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:02,313
All right.

547
00:43:02,313 --> 00:43:05,190
Wait for me here. I'll go and buy some for you.

548
00:43:22,640 --> 00:43:24,330
Why are you in tears?

549
00:43:24,330 --> 00:43:26,280
I'm going. Wait for me.

550
00:44:20,670 --> 00:44:22,403
Mom!

551
00:44:27,100 --> 00:44:32,533
Mom!

552
00:44:37,480 --> 00:44:43,073
Mom! Mom!

553
00:46:12,100 --> 00:46:14,050
Thank goodness, you are all right.

554
00:46:14,050 --> 00:46:16,200
I had a hard time finding you.

555
00:46:16,200 --> 00:46:18,440
Don't ever leave me again.

556
00:46:21,360 --> 00:46:25,110
For the whole of her life, she's been freewheeling and unrestrained

557
00:46:25,110 --> 00:46:27,940
while going through so much suffering.

558
00:46:27,940 --> 00:46:31,280
She had no qualms about receiving the wrong treatment again and again

559
00:46:31,280 --> 00:46:35,390
just because love is the only thing that ties her down in her heart.

560
00:46:35,390 --> 00:46:41,010
I hope she can have a new lease of life from her reunion with Jiahui this time.

561
00:46:44,460 --> 00:46:49,443
Many visitors come with the same question: Why?

562
00:46:49,443 --> 00:46:53,340
Why them? Why so?

563
00:46:53,340 --> 00:46:56,103
They are confused, upset,

564
00:46:56,103 --> 00:47:00,660
angry, fearful, and resentful.

565
00:47:00,660 --> 00:47:03,330
They are powerless and helpless.

566
00:47:03,330 --> 00:47:09,870
During this past period of time, I've become more aware of what I am here for.

567
00:47:09,870 --> 00:47:15,280
As a psychological counselor, I can't give an exact answer to their question.

568
00:47:15,280 --> 00:47:18,430
I must accompany them to look for the answer,

569
00:47:18,430 --> 00:47:21,390
helping them to see themselves, understand themselves,

570
00:47:21,390 --> 00:47:24,530
accept themselves and change themselves.

571
00:47:24,530 --> 00:47:29,780
I hope all of us can have the courage to face our inner heart head-on.

572
00:47:29,780 --> 00:47:32,110
Thank you, Miss He.

573
00:47:32,110 --> 00:47:34,310
I feel much more comfortable at heart.

574
00:47:34,310 --> 00:47:37,530
Miss He, thank you for helping me.

575
00:47:37,530 --> 00:47:40,560
Miss He, thank you for helping me find my courage again.

576
00:47:40,560 --> 00:47:44,520
Miss He, upon hearing what you said, I'm full of fighting spirit now.

577
00:47:44,520 --> 00:47:48,053
Miss He, I thank you from the bottom of my heart.

578
00:47:48,053 --> 00:47:50,320
Thank you, Miss He.

579
00:47:50,320 --> 00:47:53,351
Your support really matters a lot to me.

580
00:47:59,600 --> 00:48:02,710
I am He Dun, a psychological counselor.

581
00:48:02,710 --> 00:48:07,590
If you have any emotional problems in the future, feel free to come to me.

582
00:48:08,420 --> 00:48:12,580
Feeling blue? Let's talk.

